</ul>
</li>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#installing-and-running-the-devel-branch-from-source" id="id32">Installing and running the <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">devel</span></code> branch from source</a></p>
<ul>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#installing-devel-from-github-with-pip" id="id33">Installing <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">devel</span></code> from GitHub with <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">pip</span></code></a></p></li>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#installing-devel-from-github-by-cloning" id="id34">Installing <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">devel</span></code> from GitHub by cloning</a></p></li>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#running-the-devel-branch-from-a-clone" id="id35">Running the <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">devel</span></code> branch from a clone</a></p></li>
</ul>
</li>
