<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#installing-argcomplete-with-apt" id="id40">Installing <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">argcomplete</span></code> with <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">apt</span></code></a></p></li>
